Am I ready for grad school?
 
Still on the fence about going to grad school? Check out these pointers to decide if going to grad school is the right decision for you
Am I Ready for Grad School?















Explore Rinker Campus
Rinker Campus is the home of Chapman’s health science graduate programs and research at Chapman. Located in a healthcare hub made up of hospitals, labs, and medical and pharmaceutical businesses in Irvine, California, the Rinker Campus is equipped with innovative research and study spaces, patient-care labs and more.
Learn More about Rinker Campus























Tour Rinker Campus from Wherever You Are
Check out our labs, classrooms and more with this 360-degree virtual tour of our Rinker Campus in Irvine, CA.
Launch Health Sciences Study Commons Tour















Integrated Programs
Earn your graduate degree in just one year with our Integrated programs. These programs are available to current Chapman undergraduate students only.
Explore Integrated Programs








Financial Aid
Looking for financial aid information? You can find all your options on our Financial Aid page.
Explore Financial Aid







Events
We hold events and information sessions all year long. They’re a great way to learn more about grad school and get connected.
Attend an Event







Stay Connected
 
Fill out this one-minute form to stay in touch with Chapman. We'll deliver all the latest news and updates straight to your email inbox.



Stay in Touch
